---
title: Southern-Style Smothered Pork Chops with Smashed Potatoes and Broccoli
description: You'll find classic comfort in this meal inspired by Southern soul food. Savoury gravy smothers juicy pork chops, creamy smashed potatoes and tender, garlicky broccoli!
